{"name":"Benjamin Korolev","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vanguards, Snowchester","alignment":"Chaotic Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"mage armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"112 (15d8 + 45)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"20","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Radioactive","desc":"At the start of their turn, all creatures exposed to radiation take [1d8] radiant damage for every stack of radiation they have. They then lose a stack of radiation."},{"name":"Half-Life","desc":"All creatures in [MON]'s fission ring do not lose stacks of radiation."},{"name":"Mutually Assured Destruction","desc":"If [MON] dies, his atomic bombs (centered on Snowchester) explode within [2d4] minutes."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two weapon attacks."},{"name":"Plutonium Sword","desc":"[MON] swings his sword dipped in Uranium. [DEX ATK + 1] to hit. A creature is exposed to [1d4] stacks of radiation."},{"name":"Neutron Blaster","desc":"[MON] fires a powerful plutonium particle beam at a creature within 90/180ft. [DEX ATK + 1] to hit. A creature is exposed to [1d4] stacks of radiation."},{"name":"Fission","desc":"[MON] creates a radioactive ring with a 10ft. radius around himself (requires concentration). All creatures that start their turn or enter the ring gains a stack of radiation."},{"name":"Ground Zero","desc":"[MON] launches one of Snowchester's missile silos to unleash a weapon of mass destruction that will probably change the D&D World forever."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Flash of Genius","desc":"[MON] may add [INT] to any failed saving throw or ability checks. ([INT SAVE - 11]x / long rest)"}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"investigation","stat":"int"},{"name":"sleight of Hand","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Benjamin","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}